'''Nessem Shipyards''' was a large company that specialized in the production of large [[Starship/Legends|starships]]. The company was headquartered on a large [[Space station/Legends|space station]] above the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Nessem]]. The shipyards were so large that residence halls for the workers on the station appeared as small towns.

